:However... the WRT-383U is shown with colored Ethernet jacks (blue for WAN, yellow for LAN).. while the WRT-372U is shown with black Ethernet jacks. The WRT-383U is also shown as using a 12V 1A power adapter versus the WRT-372U's 5V 2.5A adapter. *[http://www.geeks.com/details.asp?invtid=LNWR300N-FB On '''geeks.com''']
